    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A loud noise erupts from a point of your choice within range. Each creature in a 10-foot-radius Sphere centered there makes a Constitution saving throw, taking [[/damage 3d8 thunder]] damage on a failed save or half as much damage on a successful one. A Construct has Disadvantage on the save.</p><p>A nonmagical object that isn't being worn or carried also takes the damage if it's in the spell's area.</p><p><strong>Using a Higher-Level Spell Slot.</strong> The damage increases by 1d8 for each spell slot level above 2.</p>",
